                vlogs.add(HealthVlogs("https://www.anytimefitness.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/AdobeStock_100525473-1536x1024.jpeg","Quick HIIT: A 20-Minute HIIT Elliptical Routine","Tired of trotting along on the treadmill to start your strength training workout every time you go to the gym? You’re not alone. While treadmills are a super intuitive and simple cardio machine, (just hop on and start walking or running,) a favorite of many personal trainers and fitness experts, and a great way to get the job done, maybe you’d like to mix up your warm up, veer from that straight line you’re used to, and get your cardio on in a whole new way? Say “hello” to the elliptical.","https://www.anytimefitness.com/ccc/workouts/quick-hiit-a-20-minute-hiit-elliptical-routine/"))

